{"tid":253714,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"6月頭鹿兒島 指宿 宮崎 行程求評","createTime":"2017-05-22T15:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T15:49:39.000Z","uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5358100484b04c6bb4a2a221d399e204eb46c283","tid":253714,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"第一次獨遊 仲要去啲交通無咁方便既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日 6點到 鹿兒島中央食+瞓<br />\n第二日 城山-&gt;櫻島/仙巖園-&gt;行吓天文館<br />\n第三日 大西山-&gt;燈塔-&gt;指宿砂浴-&gt;屋台村<br />\n第四日 JR去宮崎-&gt;青島神社-&gt;平和台公園-&gt;唔知有咩做<br />\n第五日 堀切峠-&gt;日南Sun Messe-&gt;鵜戶神宮-&gt;飫肥城-&gt;宮崎<br />\n第六日 宮崎搭10點巴士（下一班1點 好似係）-&gt;鹿兒島空港 1630機<br />\n<br />\n第六日好驚架巴士滿座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無得預約<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428f8e0a7048bcc14cd9bac791ac6c5b157e5262","tid":253714,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會太chur"},{"pid":"8eed4348134e89996e613bf0c548ae465fd4ae39","tid":253714,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897f3c4ad7c95f6453ba4635a557e783a239972","tid":253714,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42a3cf11e55b3ce951b3a9857261f4fb77a762f","tid":253714,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"